<?php
return ['messages'=>['<h5><a href="https://eji.com.hk/stage/our-inspiring-visit-to-evangel-childrens-home/">Our Inspiring Visit to Evangel Children\'s Home</a></h5>'=>'<h5><a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/our-inspiring-visit-to-evangel-childrens-home/">探訪播道兒童之家</a></h5>','<p><strong><big>Follow us</big></strong></p>'=>'<p><strong><big>關注我們</big></strong></p>','<p>Amidst our busy business work schedule, we never forget our responsibilities and commitment to our role as a pillar in the community. Our ongoing partnership with <a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/">Evangel Children’s Home</a> is a cornerstone of this commitment, allowing us to support and uplift some of the most vulnerable members of society – children who come from challenging backgrounds.</p>'=>'<p>即使工作繁忙，EJI團隊始終不忘支援社區的承諾。 我們與<a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/">播道兒童之家</a>的長期合作是這份承諾的核心：支持社會中脆弱的群體——來自困難背景的兒童，是我們作為企業的責任。</p>','<p>On this beautiful day on June 29, after all our demanding show schedule from the first half of the year, our dedicated volunteering team had the privilege of visiting the Evangel Children’s Home - a tradition that continues to enrich both our hearts and those of the children we meet. We once again engaged in a delightful ink art painting workshop centered around the theme of <em>Love in In</em>k, <em>Sparrows and Lychee </em>(「我愛水墨—天與地」) and reconnected with the children. Laughter and joy filled the space, the visit not only brought out smiles, but also sparked immense creativity among the young children.</p>'=>'<p>在6月29日，EJI義工隊有幸再次探訪播道兒童之家，延續這一溫暖傳統。 此行我們舉辦了一場以「<em>我愛水墨—天與地</em>」為主題的<em>水墨畫工作坊</em>，與孩子們重聚，展開創作。 這次探訪不僅帶來笑容，更激發了孩子們無限的創造力。</p>','<p>This year, we proudly announce a significant enhancement to our support for the Evangel Children’s Home. We have committed to being one of the primary donors for the<a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/en/services/day-care-service-sen/"> SEN 3.0 project</a>. This initiative will focus on enhancing daycare services for children with special educational needs (SEN), aiming to provide targeted support that fosters their growth and development in nurturing environments.</p>
<p>Looking ahead, we are excited to continue this heartwarming journey with Evangel Children’s Home, filled with more creativity, commitment, and positive support in the years to come.</p>
<p>We extend our heartfelt thanks to everyone who made this visit a memorable and joyful day!</p>'=>'<p>今年，我們將進一步加強對播道兒童之家的支持， 成為其「<a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/en/services/day-care-service-sen/">SEN 3.0計劃</a>」的主要捐助者之一。 這項計劃將專注於加強對有特殊教育需要 （SEN） 兒童的日托服務，旨在提供有針對性的支持，促進他們在養育環境中的成長和發展。</p>
<p>展望未來，我們期待與播道兒童之家繼續這段溫暖旅程；以更多創意、承諾與積極支持，豐富彼此。</p>
<p>我們衷心感謝所有讓這次探訪難忘和快樂的人！</p>','A Day of Art and Inspiration'=>'藝術與靈感的一天','About Evangel Children’s Home​'=>'關於播道兒童之家','Continuous Support with SEN 3.0'=>'SEN 3.0 的持續支援','Evangel Children’s Home (ECH) was established in 1956 and founded by Ms Ruth Sundquist, an American missionary from the US Evangelical Free Church. ECH has been committed to supporting the healthy growth of orphans, children and youth from broken families or families with difficult backgrounds.'=>'播道兒童之家（ECH）由美國福音自由教會傳教士Ruth Sundquist女士於1956年創立，致力於協助孤兒、破碎家庭或背景困難的兒童及青少年健康成長。 ','Read more'=>'閱讀更多','description_text-image-box-f5a9acc'=>'播道兒童之家（ECH）由美國福音自由教會傳教士Ruth Sundquist女士於1956年創立，致力於協助孤兒、破碎家庭或背景困難的兒童及青少年健康成長。 ','editor-text-editor-199946b'=>'<p><strong><big>關注我們</big></strong></p>','editor-text-editor-29e0b6c'=>'<p>在6月29日，EJI義工隊有幸再次探訪播道兒童之家，延續這一溫暖傳統。 此行我們舉辦了一場以「<em>我愛水墨—天與地</em>」為主題的<em>水墨畫工作坊</em>，與孩子們重聚，展開創作。 這次探訪不僅帶來笑容，更激發了孩子們無限的創造力。</p>','editor-text-editor-b81cfc8'=>'<p>即使工作繁忙，EJI團隊始終不忘支援社區的承諾。 我們與<a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/">播道兒童之家</a>的長期合作是這份承諾的核心：支持社會中脆弱的群體——來自困難背景的兒童，是我們作為企業的責任。</p>','editor-text-editor-dc4d231'=>'<p>今年，我們將進一步加強對播道兒童之家的支持， 成為其「<a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/en/services/day-care-service-sen/">SEN 3.0計劃</a>」的主要捐助者之一。 這項計劃將專注於加強對有特殊教育需要 （SEN） 兒童的日托服務，旨在提供有針對性的支持，促進他們在養育環境中的成長和發展。</p>
<p>展望未來，我們期待與播道兒童之家繼續這段溫暖旅程；以更多創意、承諾與積極支持，豐富彼此。</p>
<p>我們衷心感謝所有讓這次探訪難忘和快樂的人！</p>','https://www.ech.org.hk/'=>'https://www.ech.org.hk/','tabs-tab_content-f479391-094376b'=>'<h5><a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/our-inspiring-visit-to-evangel-childrens-home/">探訪播道兒童之家</a></h5>','tabs-tab_title-f479391-094376b'=>'閱讀更多','title-heading-0a4699f'=>'SEN 3.0 的持續支援','title-heading-9eca9f0'=>'藝術與靈感的一天','title_text-image-box-f5a9acc'=>'關於播道兒童之家','url-image-box-f5a9acc'=>'https://www.ech.org.hk/']];
